window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It’s all smoke and mirrors until someone breaks the glass.</b></p> <p>Lilith’s invitation to the Underealm has thrown us for a loop. Impossible to hide from danger if danger has ordered an audience.</p> <p>It’ll be the wedding of the century, an alliance bringing peace to the Underealm, but if Lilith recognises who I am, it could be the end of me. Thank goodness for Cora and her plan - smoke and mirrors and deception.</p> <p>Let’s hope it works, otherwise, if the journey doesn’t kill me, Lilith will.</p> <p><b><i>A kickass urban fantasy with a why choose romance. Vampires, ghosts, angels, and demons. Perfect for listeners who enjoy forbidden romance, enemies to lovers, or friends to lovers.</i></b></p>"; 
